865
00:53:44,250 --> 00:53:45,250
Sarah!

866
00:53:49,875 --> 00:53:51,000
Sarah!

867
00:54:02,916 --> 00:54:03,916
Sarah?

868
00:54:06,583 --> 00:54:07,666
Sarah!

869
00:54:10,083 --> 00:54:12,375
