921
00:59:15,916 --> 00:59:17,750
No, no!

922
00:59:17,833 --> 00:59:20,958
-[Sarah sobbing]
-[crowd commotion]

923
00:59:30,583 --> 00:59:33,125
[dramatic drumming]

924
00:59:36,958 --> 00:59:40,208
[dramatic music playing]

925
00:59:46,583 --> 00:59:48,125
[chains clanking]

926
00:59:55,625 --> 00:59:58,333
[Elijah] The penalty
for practicing witchcraft

927
00:59:58,916 --> 01:00:00,375
is death by hanging!

928
01:00:00,458 --> 01:00:02,625
[crowd shouting] Hang them!

929
01:00:02,708 --> 01:00:04,166
Hang them!

930
01:00:04,250 --> 01:00:06,333
[commotion]

931
01:00:06,416 --> 01:00:07,625
Confess!

932
01:00:09,375 --> 01:00:12,375
Confess your sins or burn in eternal hell.

933
01:00:13,500 --> 01:00:15,666
-[woman 1] Hang her!
-[Elijah] Confess!

934
01:00:17,583 --> 01:00:18,666
Confess!

935
01:00:20,833 --> 01:00:21,750
Confess!

936
01:00:22,333 --> 01:00:23,750
[man 2] Hang them!

937
01:00:23,833 --> 01:00:27,541
[melancholic music playing]

938
01:00:27,625 --> 01:00:30,666
[indistinct]

939
01:00:39,166 --> 01:00:42,000
[whispers] I confess. [gasps]

940
01:00:43,875 --> 01:00:45,625
No! No!

941
01:00:45,708 --> 01:00:47,375
I confess!

942
01:00:48,041 --> 01:00:51,416
