[screams]

1087
01:11:14,083 --> 01:11:17,000
[grunting wildly]

1088
01:11:17,916 --> 01:11:19,833
[Sam grunting]

1089
01:11:19,916 --> 01:11:21,291
[Christine gasps]

1090
01:11:21,375 --> 01:11:22,916
Oh, Jesus Christ!

1091
01:11:23,000 --> 01:11:27,000
