1114
01:12:27,083 --> 01:12:28,416
we have to kill him.

1115
01:12:30,708 --> 01:12:32,166
We need to kill Nick Goode.

1116
01:12:34,916 --> 01:12:37,541
But I called him… I thought…

1117
01:12:39,583 --> 01:12:40,833
