1118
01:12:41,875 --> 01:12:43,750
We need to go. Now!

1119
01:12:44,250 --> 01:12:47,166
[grunting]

1120
01:12:49,041 --> 01:12:50,375
[Deena grunts]

1121
01:12:54,625 --> 01:12:57,416
[Deena panting]

1122
01:12:58,791 --> 01:13:00,750
