1155
01:14:42,625 --> 01:14:43,666
Carrie, cool.

1156
01:14:45,083 --> 01:14:46,250
We'll Carrie him.

1157
01:14:48,625 --> 01:14:50,541
[buzzing]

1158
01:14:52,375 --> 01:14:55,708
[dramatic music playing]

1159
01:14:55,791 --> 01:14:58,458
[imitating machine gun]

1160
01:14:58,541 --> 01:14:59,791
[Martin blows raspberry]

1161
01:15:01,750 --> 01:15:02,958
Seriously?

1162
