1171
01:15:36,250 --> 01:15:38,750
We're gonna kill Sheriff Goode
and save Shadyside.

1172
01:15:39,416 --> 01:15:40,416
[inhales deeply]

1173
01:15:41,083 --> 01:15:41,916
OK.

