1180
01:16:04,333 --> 01:16:05,250
Dig!

1181
01:16:05,333 --> 01:16:08,166
-[digging]
-[Cindy and Ziggy gasping]

1182
01:16:08,250 --> 01:16:09,375
Get ready to run.

1183
