-[Cindy] Let's go!

1184
01:16:13,791 --> 01:16:14,958
[Christine gasps]

1185
01:16:18,000 --> 01:16:19,000
This is it.

1186
01:16:19,750 --> 01:16:20,666
Yep.

1187
01:16:23,041 --> 01:16:26,375
[tragic music playing]

1188
01:16:26,458 --> 01:16:30,125
[crowd shouting]
Hang her! Hang her! Hang her!

1189
01:16:30,208 --> 01:16:32,291
[crowd shouting]

1190
01:16:37,333 --> 01:16:41,250
[whistling jovially]

1191
01:16:43,000 --> 01:16:44,875
-[sighs]
