1248
01:20:36,375 --> 01:20:38,666
♪ Getting weapons
With the greatest of ease ♪

1249
01:20:38,750 --> 01:20:41,458
♪ The gangs stake
Their own campus locale ♪

1250
01:20:41,541 --> 01:20:45,041
♪ And if they catch you slippin'
