1252
01:20:47,583 --> 01:20:50,250
♪ They're gonna bash it up
Bash it up, bash it up ♪

1253
01:20:50,333 --> 01:20:51,333
♪ Bash it up ♪

1254
01:20:51,416 --> 01:20:53,791
♪ Hey they don't pay no mind ♪

1255
01:20:53,875 --> 01:20:56,708
♪ If you're under 18
You won't be doing any time…♪

1256
01:20:56,791 --> 01:20:58,833
-OK, cut it!
-Cut it!

1257
01:20:59,500 --> 01:21:01,083
♪ Come out and play ♪

1258
01:21:01,875 --> 01:21:03,875
[electricity whirs down]

1259
01:21:03,958 --> 01:21:05,750
[emergency lighting clicks on]

1260
01:21:16,000 --> 01:21:17,291
[bells ringing]

1261
01:21:21,166 --> 01:21:24,125
[suspenseful music playing]

1262
01:21:26,500 --> 01:21:27,416
[both panting]

1263
01:21:27,500 --> 01:21:29,083
[whispering] I don't see anyone.

1264
01:21:29,166 --> 01:21:30,291
[Deena gasps]

1265
01:21:31,333 --> 01:21:32,625
I see Martin and Ziggy!

1266
01:21:34,708 --> 01:21:36,000
[Martin] Jesus, careful!

1267
01:21:40,750 --> 01:21:41,958
-Be quiet!
-[Martin] Why?

1268
01:21:42,041 --> 01:21:43,333
There's someone here!

1269
01:21:44,208 --> 01:21:47,458
[suspenseful music playing]

1270
01:21:49,500 --> 01:21:50,875
[gasping]

1271
01:21:55,041 --> 01:21:57,458
Police! Hands up! Hands up!

1272
01:21:57,541 --> 01:21:59,875
Listen! You don't have any idea
what's going on!

1273
01:21:59,958 --> 01:22:01,916
You're gonna die
if you don't listen to me!

1274
01:22:02,000 --> 01:22:02,958
[squealing] We cool.

1275
01:22:04,291 --> 01:22:05,208
Martin?

1276
01:22:05,291 --> 01:22:06,416
Yeah, yeah!

1277
01:22:06,500 --> 01:22:08,041
Are you kidding me?

1278
01:22:08,125 --> 01:22:11,791
[police radio] Stolen vehicle located at
Shadyside Mall. Officers scan Shadyside…

1279
01:22:11,875 --> 01:22:13,583
[male cop 2] Hey, freeze! Freeze!

1280
01:22:14,083 --> 01:22:15,500
I got two more over here!

1281
01:22:16,708 --> 01:22:17,958
Drop your weapon!

1282
01:22:18,041 --> 01:22:20,083
Sir, sir, just please let us explain!

1283
01:22:20,166 --> 01:22:22,416
[male cop 2] Drop your weapon!

1284
01:22:23,833 --> 01:22:25,250
Slide it to me.

1285
01:22:30,000 --> 01:22:31,791
We got the 5150--

1286
01:22:31,875 --> 01:22:33,125
[grunts]

1287
01:22:34,666 --> 01:22:35,916
[knife whooshes]

1288
01:22:37,916 --> 01:22:39,375
[Martin screams] Oh!

1289
01:22:42,583 --> 01:22:44,833
-[Martin] Oh my! Holy…
-[Christine] We gotta go!

1290
01:22:44,916 --> 01:22:46,708
-[Martin] What is that?
-[male cop 2] Kapinski!

1291
01:22:47,375 --> 01:22:48,541
[gunshots]

1292
01:22:50,125 --> 01:22:52,250
-Bastard!
-[gun clicks empty]

1293
01:22:56,708 --> 01:22:57,708
[male cop 2] No!

1294
01:22:57,791 --> 01:22:58,958
[Martin yells]

1295
01:22:59,041 --> 01:23:03,041
OK. I need you to focus
because the plan is still on, OK?

1296
01:23:03,125 --> 01:23:05,875
-Wait, wait, wait. You're leaving?
-Hold fast.

1297
01:23:05,958 --> 01:23:09,750
Stay out of their way.
They'll walk right by you.

1298
01:23:09,833 --> 01:23:10,833
[knife whooshes]

1299
01:23:12,333 --> 01:23:13,708
Oh! Goodness gracious!

1300
01:23:17,958 --> 01:23:20,833
[panting] Please be careful! OK?

