1310
01:24:15,166 --> 01:24:18,416
[Sam grunting]

1311
01:24:23,250 --> 01:24:25,958
[suspenseful music playing]

1312
01:24:28,125 --> 01:24:29,208
[exhales]

1313
01:24:33,750 --> 01:24:35,250
[killer breathes loudly]

1314
